node.text: Today Is my birthday and I am 23 years old. Did we eat too much cake? Of course! did we have to much fun... NEVER lol. Guys I was surrounded by friends and family and made a bunch of horsepower. It was a good one!

node.text:
New Video LIVE on YouTube! So @dodgeofficial gave me a Widebody Hellcat Redeye! To modify however we want to drag Race at Roadkill Nights on Woodward Ave in Michigan So obviously the 1st thing I had to do was put Bull Horns on it for more Areodynamics lol.

 I never thought I would get the opportunity to be in this event and just have to thank the guys at @dodgeofficial and @roadkillshow Aug 14th on Woodward Ave come out and see us

node.text: BIG ANNOUNCEMENT: Guys we got invited by @dodgeofficial @motortrend and @roadkillshow to attend Roadkill Nights! AND Drag race I have always been a massive fan of Roadkill and remember watching the 1st Roadkill nights event they ever had. I never thought I would have the ability or opportunity to be in something like this but here we are! And I am super excited for this event Aug 14th is the date save it come out we need as much Redneck support as we can get lol.

node.text: 1500Hp twin turbo Cop Car. Ya I like the sound of that!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Westen champlin in Cowley County, Kansas. May be an image of car and road.

node.text: Well guys the Smoke-Stang hit the track for the 1st time. Look she was so excited she was throwing flames out the stack! And we might have blown up the amazon special intercooler. But if I didnt break at least one thing it wouldn't been a natural westen day. New video live on YouTube

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Westen champlin on May 05, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and outdoors.

node.text: Guys 2 years ago when I started making videos if you would have told me that @grangersmith was gonna throw me the keys to his truck to go rip around the Yee Yee Farm. And that I would be in a music video well I would have told you to back off the cotton candy lol but here we are it's a reality🤯🤯🥳🥳

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Westen champlin in Cowley County, Kansas. May be an image of one or more people, beard, outdoors and text that says 'Ok Westen last chance! where are the donuts?'.

node.text: Ok officer your not gonna believe this. But there I was and then here came Bigfoot.....

node.text: I might be crazy for letting a kid I have never seen drive. Jump in my car I have put so much work and time into. but once I seen that excitement and that smile it was worth every second! In the end all we will have is memory's so let's make good ones.
